<paragraph id="8BCADC5EBA0B290BFF61FBF7FA97FB6F" blockId="4.[151,1437,717,2026]" pageId="4" pageNumber="56">
<emphasis id="B901004CBA0B290BFF61FBF7FEB7FB87" bold="true" box="[198,355,1117,1143]" pageId="4" pageNumber="56">Recognition.</emphasis>
This genus and species may be distinguished from other North American empidoids by its yellow colour, bare eyes, lack of distinct acrostichals and the postpedicel with dense grey pubescence.
</paragraph>
